### Get all books
GET http://localhost:5034/api/books
Accept: application/json

###

### Get one book by ID
GET http://localhost:5034/api/books/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new book
POST http://localhost:5034/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Refactoring",
  "author": "Martin Fowler",
  "price": 50.00,
  "stock": 7
}

###

### Update an existing book
PUT http://localhost:5034/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code (Updated Edition)",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "price": 37.50,
  "stock": 15
}

###

### Delete a book
DELETE http://localhost:5034/api/books/2

###

### Try to get a deleted or non-existent book (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:5034/api/books/99
Accept: application/json
